commit.message:
fix: split @theme inline into @theme for semantic tokens

@theme inline inlines values directly into utilities, so overriding CSS
variables in .dark had no effect. Move semantic color/shadow tokens to
@theme (non-inline) so utilities reference CSS custom properties that
dark mode can override at runtime.

